race.comment: ANTHROPOLOGY (5) looks hard to beat on what she showed on debut. Was strongly supported at Mackay and after drifting back found the line well for fourth. Has upside and this is easier. Expected to run well. SCARLET HAZE (11) is a former NSW galloper who had one run in Newcastle when she showed speed and weakened late. Makes returns for a new yard and will find this easier. Blinkers added and expected to give a sight. BADLIFEDECISION (6) was safely held fresh at Mackay but has since won a trial by a space. Expecting a better run this time. YES LARRY (4) is a gelding by Worthy Cause from Argento Perlo on debut. Won a recent Dalby trial and stable strike-rate with debutantes is strong. Worth watching for a move.
